description: A proposed new deal could see customers pay up to 12.6% less for natural gas, if Tynwald agrees.
title: Isle of Man gas bills could fall under new agreement
title_page: Isle of Man gas bills could fall under new agreement - BBC News
maintext: "We're not looking for a short-term fix, and at the end of this I don't want to be grateful for anything, I'm only asking for what I'm entitled to."
